beer.beer_description: Crafted with Hallertau Hersbrucker hops and four specialty malts – carared, melanodium, caramunich (crystal) and wheat this amber ale has biscuity and toffee malt flavours that linger on the front palate. The relative sweetness is perfectly balanced by a traditional ale yeast and hop combination.
